{"tid":849818,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"帽事？","createTime":"2018-10-06T03:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T03:52:39.000Z","uid":141725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebafedefaf765e121223b263fecd4371d003539","tid":849818,"uid":141725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"吉普車闖流浮山軍事區域賞夜景 衝落50米山坡釀3傷<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=UOe6E5NqDY%2Bf96mpHv%2FyZ6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=cc2e7593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網 &middot; 8,624人追蹤<br />\n3 小時前<br />\n吉普車衝落50米山坡男司機及2母子受傷，現場豎有警告牌。（沈厚錚攝）<br />\n吉普車衝落50米山坡男司機及2母子受傷，現場豎有警告牌。（沈厚錚攝）<br />\n一名50歲姓黎男子駕駛白色吉普車，載同46歲姓竇女友人及其18歲姓麥兒子，今日(6日)凌晨1時許，駛至流浮山稔灣路通往軍事區域的無名山路賞夜景，男司機褪車落斜時，疑因現場環境昏暗，吉普車失事衝落50米山坡下，車上3人俱受傷被困車內，於是報警求助。消防到場游繩落山，將他們救回路邊，男司機頭傷及胸痛；母子2人分別頸、手腳及頸、腰、手腳受傷，乘救護車送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n意外現場附近豎有「落彈區域，嚴禁入內」的警告牌。由於肇事吉普車飛墮於草叢中，現場昏暗，故需待今早召拖車拖返路面。警員正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一名50歲姓黎男子駕駛白色吉普車，載同46歲姓竇女友人及其18歲姓麥兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}